overview: The business is prospering day by day thanks to Seo-Jun, the CEO of ASMR startup, whose success is thanks to the wife of a conglomerate, and Su-Hyeok, his employee, and groundbreaking ideas and lively recording skills. However, there was a fatal secret to the lively ASMR recording... What is the secret of the chemistry between the male voice actors Seo Jun & Soo Hyuk and the female voice actors Yuri & Jung Sook with a great body?
title: Yaseol ASMR
